<main>
    <section class="product-main">
        <div class="product-gallery">
            <div class="main-image">
                <img src="{{ 'conditioning-creme.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Conditioning Creme">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-details">
            <p class="subtitle">Nourishing Ritual</p>
            <h1>Conditioning Creme</h1>
            <div class="description">A luxurious, moisture-locking creme designed to restore hair elasticity and deliver a weightless silk finish. Infused with Shea Butter and Hydrolyzed Keratin, it seals the cuticle and protects against environmental stressors.</div>
            <div class="price">Rs. 1,650</div>

            <div class="bundle-selector">
                <div class="bundle-card selected">
                    <div class="bundle-info">
                        <h4>Single Jar</h4>
                        <p>250ml - Daily Hydration</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bundle-price">Rs. 1,650</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bundle-card">
                    <div class="bundle-info">
                        <h4>The Duo Pack</h4>
                        <p>2 Jars - Deep Therapy</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bundle-price">Rs. 3,000</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button class="atc-btn" onclick="gAddToCart('{{ product.variants.first.id }}', this)">Add to Ritual</button>

            <div class="accordion">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">Ingredients <span>+</span></button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Behentrimonium Chloride, Vitamin E, Silk Amino Acids.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">How to Use <span>+</span></button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">After cleansing with Avyen Scalp Cleanse, apply from mid-lengths to ends. Leave for 3-5 minutes for deep penetration. Rinse with cool water to seal the shine.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">The Result <span>+</span></button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">Instant detangling, reduced frizz, and a velvet-soft texture that lasts all day without weighing your hair down.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="community-section">
        <h2>Loved by Our Community</h2>
        <div class="community-grid">
            <div class="community-item">
                <img src="{{ 'conditioner-model.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Avyen Community" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;">
            </div>
            <div class="community-item">
                <img src="{{ 'conditioner-pump-1.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Avyen Community" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;">
            </div>
            <div class="community-item">
                <img src="{{ 'conditioner-pump-2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Avyen Community" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;">
            </div>
            <div class="community-item">
                <img src="{{ 'texture.jpeg' | asset_url }}" alt="Avyen Texture" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-grid" style="background: #f9f9f9;">
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h2>Weightless Hydration</h2>
            <p>Our micro-emulsion technology allows nutrients to penetrate the hair shaft without leaving a greasy residue, maintaining natural volume.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
             <div class="feature-image">
                 <img src="{{ 'plate-conditioner.jpeg' | asset_url }}" alt="Weightless Hydration" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;">
             </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-item">
             <div class="feature-image">
                 <div style="width:100%; height:100%; background:#eee; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#666;">REPAIR IMAGE</div>
             </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h2>Cuticle Repair</h2>
            <p>Hydrolyzed Keratin fills in the gaps of damaged hair cuticles, smoothing the surface and preventing future breakage and split ends.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h2>FAQ</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">Should I apply conditioner to my scalp? <span>+</span></button>
                <div class="faq-answer">We recommend applying Conditioning Creme from mid-lengths to ends. The scalp already produces natural oils; focusing on the ends prevents weighing hair down.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">How long should I leave it in? <span>+</span></button>
                <div class="faq-answer">For daily use, 2-3 minutes is sufficient. For a deep treatment, leave it on for 5-10 minutes before rinsing with cool water.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">Is it suitable for fine hair? <span>+</span></button>
                <div class="faq-answer">Absolutely. Our formula is lightweight and won't leave your hair feeling greasy or flat if rinsed thoroughly.</div>
            </div>
